exd6 8. Qd2 { We plan to castle and target the d6 pawn which is quite weak. }
8... d5 9. O-O-O { Pestering the d-pawn. } 9... Be6 10. Ng5
{ And Black is clearly worse here as he cannot move the e6 Bishop. } *

