6... e6
{ Looks logical as now  6...e5  doesn't make sense. Everywhere else Black has both these options of 6...e6 and 6...e5 but only here it narrows down to one that is 6...e6 as with the Bishop on g5 already, it would look dubious to weaken the d5 square since the f6 Knight is already pinned. }
