{ A logical move towards the centre. There are some funky or offbeat lines like   2.Qe2  stopping ...d5 but then Black can play  2...c5  transposing to a Sicilian where our Queen is not ideally placed on e2 but nevertheless it has been tried and tested in many top-level games as it avoids heaps of theoretical debates. But let's stick to the principled option here. :@@EndBracket@@ }
